summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to and amending Plat 11E, Page 54 of the Official Zoning Map of The City of Seattle, Ordinance 86300, to rezone certain property located on the south side of Northwest 65th Street, 78 feet west of 20th Avenue Northwest from Duplex Residence High Density (RD 5000) Zone to Neighborhood Business (BN) Zone and accepting a Property Use and Development Agreement in connection therewith. (Petition of Hamilton Eckert, C.F. 288620).
